  "detailed_description": "Lani's Call: A Tiny Whale Singer Story is a 10 min game experience where you can play with Lani, a playful humpback whale, who dives into action when an earthshaking event threatens her underwater home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/45c48163c72f98ec18b25ef7711dd683.avif?t=1749215606\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide Lani through vibrant coral reefs, dense seaweed jungles, and dark ocean depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/be570af36cf0dbea6267f6089d4a8a1c.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/be570af36cf0dbea6267f6089d4a8a1c.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Call out with Lani's voice to commune with other humpbacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/b4a4a2054bcd6967d8efcbfc6c97e2ab.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/b4a4a2054bcd6967d8efcbfc6c97e2ab.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Take advantage of Lani's massive size to rescue smaller creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/ee71de161aa6057a04049cf377891900.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/ee71de161aa6057a04049cf377891900.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Discover what lies at the end of the glimmering trail...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/cac690aac98aa5b52f806f249ed2920a.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/cac690aac98aa5b52f806f249ed2920a.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>This cosy, emotional adventure offers a heartfelt introduction to the richly woven WHALE SINGER universe.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "Lani's Call: A Tiny Whale Singer Story is a 10 min game experience where you can play with Lani, a playful humpback whale, who dives into action when an earthshaking event threatens her underwater home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/45c48163c72f98ec18b25ef7711dd683.avif?t=1749215606\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide Lani through vibrant coral reefs, dense seaweed jungles, and dark ocean depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/be570af36cf0dbea6267f6089d4a8a1c.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/be570af36cf0dbea6267f6089d4a8a1c.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Call out with Lani's voice to commune with other humpbacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/b4a4a2054bcd6967d8efcbfc6c97e2ab.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/b4a4a2054bcd6967d8efcbfc6c97e2ab.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Take advantage of Lani's massive size to rescue smaller creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/ee71de161aa6057a04049cf377891900.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/ee71de161aa6057a04049cf377891900.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Discover what lies at the end of the glimmering trail...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/cac690aac98aa5b52f806f249ed2920a.poster.avif?t=1749215606\" width=427 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494560/extras/cac690aac98aa5b52f806f249ed2920a.webm?t=1749215606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>This cosy, emotional adventure offers a heartfelt introduction to the richly woven WHALE SINGER universe.</p>",
